<li>DOI: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1145/3276604.3276623">10.1145/3276604.3276623</a></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t6d.html"><span class="tagM">T6D: Synergies</span></a><ul><li> The paper is explicitly a vision/position piece emphasizing cross-cutting synergies and future directions.
</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t4a.html"><span class="tagL">T4A: Workbenches</span></a><ul><li> It includes substantial tool support or infrastructure relevant for engineering/using languages.
</li></ul></li>
